<Link id="l00148" /><CodeLine lineNumber="148"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// This edge kind has the same fixup expression as BranchPCRel32, but further</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00149" /><CodeLine lineNumber="149"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// identifies the call/branch as being to a pointer jump stub. For edges of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00150" /><CodeLine lineNumber="150"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// this kind the jump stub should not be bypassed (use</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00151" /><CodeLine lineNumber="151"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// BranchPCRel32ToPtrJumpStubBypassable for that), but the pointer location</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00153" /><CodeLine lineNumber="153"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00154" /><CodeLine lineNumber="154"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Fixup expression:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00155" /><CodeLine lineNumber="155"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///   Fixup &lt;- Target - Fixup + Addend : int32</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00156" /><CodeLine lineNumber="156"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00157" /><CodeLine lineNumber="157"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Errors:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00158" /><CodeLine lineNumber="158"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///   - The result of the fixup expression must fit into an int32, otherwise</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00159" /><CodeLine lineNumber="159"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///     an out-of-range error will be returned.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00160" /><CodeLine lineNumber="160"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00164" /><CodeLine lineNumber="164"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00409" /><CodeLine lineNumber="409"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Optimize the GOT and Stub relocations if the edge target address is in range</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00410" /><CodeLine lineNumber="410"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// 1 PCRel32GOTLoadRelaxable. For this edge kind, if the target is in range,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00411" /><CodeLine lineNumber="411"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// then replace GOT load with lea. (THIS IS UNIMPLEMENTED RIGHT NOW!)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00412" /><CodeLine lineNumber="412"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// 2 BranchPCRel32ToPtrJumpStubRelaxable. For this edge kind, if the target is</span></CodeLine>
